                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "你好，我是阿慕 —— 一个 35 岁的临“退”程序员，一名见习独立开发者。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.8,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-ui",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
