                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "gPmbN",
                  "name": "P 1",
                  "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "程序员生涯的进度条已快到头，下一步打算成为一名独立开发者，做自己喜欢的事，也能养家糊口。如果你也面临职业生涯的窘境，想探索新的可能，欢迎加我微信 Amuluze 交流。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.8,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-ui",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "iKhZ0",
                  "name": "P 2",
                  "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Beacon 是我作为见习独立开发者的第一款开源产品，既满足自己监控云服务器的需求，也用来锻炼独立开发的能力。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.8,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-ui",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "o2m78",
                  "name": "P 3",
                  "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "它是一款开源的云服务器监控与 Docker 容器管理工具，帮助实时掌控 CPU、内存、磁盘等资源占用，也能便捷管理部署在云服务上的容器状态。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.8,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-ui",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "OQwgI",
                  "name": "P 4",
                  "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
